# Setup Authentication and Database Schema

Sets up the foundational auth layer and DB schema for the B2B car rental platform. Covers Prisma models, JWT auth with bcrypt, a roles guard, and shared PrismaService.

## Proposed Changes

### Dependencies

#### [MODIFY] [package.json](file:///c:/Users/amine/Desktop/Liadtech/personel%20project/Ai%20Car%20Rental/backend/package.json)
Install the following packages via `npm install` (runtime):
- `@prisma/client`, `@nestjs/jwt`, `@nestjs/passport`, `@nestjs/config`, `passport`, `passport-jwt`, `bcrypt`

Install as devDependencies:
- `prisma`, `@types/bcrypt`, `@types/passport-jwt`

---

### Prisma Schema & Environment

#### [NEW] [schema.prisma](file:///c:/Users/amine/Desktop/Liadtech/personel%20project/Ai%20Car%20Rental/backend/prisma/schema.prisma)
- Defines `Role` enum: `ADMIN`, `AGENCY`
- `User` model: `id`, `email` (unique), `password`, `role` (Role), timestamps
- [Agency](file:///c:/Users/amine/Desktop/Liadtech/personel%20project/Ai%20Car%20Rental/backend/src/agency/agency.module.ts#5-10) model: one-to-one `userId` FK to `User`, `name`, `minAge`, `depositAmount`, `rentalConditions`, timestamps

#### [NEW] [.env](file:///c:/Users/amine/Desktop/Liadtech/personel%20project/Ai%20Car%20Rental/backend/.env)
```
DATABASE_URL="postgresql://USER:PASSWORD@localhost:5432/car_rental_db"
JWT_SECRET="your-super-secret-key"
```
> [!IMPORTANT]
> You must replace `USER` and `PASSWORD` with your actual PostgreSQL credentials before running migrations.

---

### Shared Prisma Module

#### [NEW] [prisma.service.ts](file:///c:/Users/amine/Desktop/Liadtech/personel%20project/Ai%20Car%20Rental/backend/src/prisma/prisma.service.ts)
Extends `PrismaClient`, connects on `onModuleInit`, disconnects on `onModuleDestroy`.

#### [NEW] [prisma.module.ts](file:///c:/Users/amine/Desktop/Liadtech/personel%20project/Ai%20Car%20Rental/backend/src/prisma/prisma.module.ts)
Global module exporting `PrismaService` for use across the app.

---

### Auth Module

#### [NEW] [login.dto.ts](file:///c:/Users/amine/Desktop/Liadtech/personel%20project/Ai%20Car%20Rental/backend/src/auth/dto/login.dto.ts)
Defines `LoginDto` with `email` and `password` fields.

#### [NEW] [jwt.strategy.ts](file:///c:/Users/amine/Desktop/Liadtech/personel%20project/Ai%20Car%20Rental/backend/src/auth/strategies/jwt.strategy.ts)
Passport `JwtStrategy` extracting Bearer token, validating against `JWT_SECRET`, returning `{ userId, email, role }` payload.

#### [MODIFY] [auth.service.ts](file:///c:/Users/amine/Desktop/Liadtech/personel%20project/Ai%20Car%20Rental/backend/src/auth/auth.service.ts)
- `login(dto)`: finds user by email, compares bcrypt hash, generates and returns a signed JWT.

#### [MODIFY] [auth.controller.ts](file:///c:/Users/amine/Desktop/Liadtech/personel%20project/Ai%20Car%20Rental/backend/src/auth/auth.controller.ts)
- `POST /auth/login`: takes `LoginDto`, returns `{ access_token }`.

#### [MODIFY] [auth.module.ts](file:///c:/Users/amine/Desktop/Liadtech/personel%20project/Ai%20Car%20Rental/backend/src/auth/auth.module.ts)
Imports `JwtModule.registerAsync` (reads `JWT_SECRET` from config), `PassportModule`, `PrismaModule`. Provides `JwtStrategy`.

---

### Common Guards & Decorators

#### [NEW] [roles.decorator.ts](file:///c:/Users/amine/Desktop/Liadtech/personel%20project/Ai%20Car%20Rental/backend/src/common/decorators/roles.decorator.ts)
`@Roles(...roles)` metadata decorator using `SetMetadata`.

#### [NEW] [roles.guard.ts](file:///c:/Users/amine/Desktop/Liadtech/personel%20project/Ai%20Car%20Rental/backend/src/common/guards/roles.guard.ts)
`RolesGuard` implementing `CanActivate`. Uses `Reflector` to read `@Roles` metadata, compares to `request.user.role`.

#### [NEW] [jwt-auth.guard.ts](file:///c:/Users/amine/Desktop/Liadtech/personel%20project/Ai%20Car%20Rental/backend/src/common/guards/jwt-auth.guard.ts)
Thin wrapper around `AuthGuard('jwt')` for clean import in controllers.

